{
  "stem": "5430.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so they allowed us to go down to middle Asia, which was warm country.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So to-- in our case was, to Kirghizia, the state Kirghizia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so they-- we went on a train that travelled south.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "First of all-- oh, before we go there, we were able to load our belongings on our flatbeds, except my father.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We all got permits.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because he was a troublemaker, they would not give him a permit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they would keep him there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So my father managed to come with us till-- I think it was Asino, that other town that hooked up to the main railroad, the Tomsk.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There he says, [INAUDIBLE]-- children-- I know I'm not going to go with you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You go, and I'll catch up with you somehow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he traveled without a permit up to Tomsk-- Tomsk or Asino, one of those two places.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he was arrested by the KBG or the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we hadn't heard from him then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We traveled-- he was put, literally, in a prison over there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "For what reason, we still don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, just because he was a leader or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so we--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We thought that was the end.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we decided to go with the rest of the [INAUDIBLE] with the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, all of Middle Asia, it was they took Tushgan and Tajikistan, they wanted us from Serbia to a warm climate, which is the southern, Middle Asia, which is Kirghizia, Uzbekistan, Tajikistan, all those warm parts of the country.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went by train down there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In the meantime, my sister decided to go off on one of the stops to get some hot water-- they always have hot water at all the stations-- to make some soup for my mother, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
